column2: SELECT   m.id AS id,    m.ra AS ra,    m.dec AS dec,   n.distance AS dist,   o.npof AS nprof,   p.profMean as prof_mean FROM MyDB.CAM_CATALOGUE AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n   JOIN photoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   JOIN photoProfile AS p on n.objid=p.objid
